{"tid":2320204,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣東部海域6.7級地震！香港有天文台亦接獲市民報告感到地震","createTime":"2020-12-10T15:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T15:28:14.000Z","uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3b72be33f680c9f705d476741a8a40594838a815","tid":2320204,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T15:16:38.000Z","msg":"台灣再傳強烈地震。今晚9時20分，台灣東北地區附近發生有感地震，初判震度4級以上地區：北部、宜蘭、中部、花蓮、竹苗。中央氣象局指地震級數為黎克特制6.7級，有指今次地震全台有感。暫時未有傷亡報告。地震也令福建福州、廈門、泉州等地有明顯震感，網民指家中吊燈等物強烈晃動。晚上9時27分，台灣東部海域、宜蘭縣政府東邊26公里也錄得4.8級餘震，震源深度為71.5公里。花蓮近海今天下午亦曾發生５.3級地震。<br />\n<br />\n香港天文台隨後亦報告台灣晚上的強烈地震，指地震級數為6.4級，並指接獲市民報告表示感到地震，天文台正進行分析，當有進一步資料時將會盡快公佈。<br />\n<br />\n中央氣象局地震測報中心主任陳國昌表示，晚間該宗地震主要發生於歐亞大陸板塊與菲律賓海板塊隱沒帶，屬於板塊隱沒帶所引起的深層地震，而該地區一直以來都是地震的好發區域，2000年到現在共發生過23宗6級以上的地震，2004年曾發生過7.1級地震。今年也已有4宗6級以上地震，先前幾宗距離台灣較遠，今晚的地震較靠近台灣，因此感受較明顯，這也是今年最強的一宗地震。陳指，不排除一周內仍有4級以上餘震發生。而近日東北部宜蘭多雨，加上地震影響，山區土石可能鬆動，建議民眾近日少前往山區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201210/NEFU37AELBDIDHP2FNJHH4DBYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201210%2FNEFU37AELBDIDHP2FNJHH4DBYQ%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=eb1dd587\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201210%2FNEFU37AELBDIDHP2FNJHH4DBYQ%2F&h=a20e5a4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201210/NEFU37AELBDIDHP2FNJHH4DBYQ/</a>"},{"pid":"35aa35ee9cecfff664fa6061c8ddedf2d8c61b25","tid":2320204,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"標題出多咗個「有」字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aba81888ddab4fec0e0f68a3c3958af49cfec00","tid":2320204,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmSxoOZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmSxoOZ.png&h=c91f20d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小北百貨的商品被震到跌落"},{"pid":"80d396b5153572200177faa2a4bcdcc104fd595a","tid":2320204,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T15:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKO4Zn3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKO4Zn3.png&h=70e6bf11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4G0fmBr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4G0fmBr.png&h=cce7b849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基隆市中山區 電線杆都倒塌"},{"pid":"281090623317a69a42bbd65582704540e7f5b5bc","tid":2320204,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T15:25:01.000Z","msg":"位在新竹市建中一路荒廢30年的危樓連城大樓，今天晚間地震時掉下大量磚塊，且老舊遮雨棚瞬間倒塌，砸中停在大樓底下的車輛，粗估至少有5輛轎車遭潑及，幸好無發生人員傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hj3gQwh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhj3gQwh.png&h=78490e8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hkiHL4C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhkiHL4C.png&h=f7a455e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"515df26f73aa079cff70e8e28bc09287872d37b4","tid":2320204,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T15:26:28.000Z","msg":"港豬：台灣好多地震 唔移民了<br />\n歐美：天氣好凍 不了"},{"pid":"c9e119fdb467a25267b9ef62970f5fa9dfb1d0b8","tid":2320204,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"515df26f73aa079cff70e8e28bc09287872d37b4","tid":2320204,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T15:26:28.000Z","msg":"港豬：台灣好多地震 唔移民了<br />\n歐美：天氣好凍 不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"以地埋位置嚟講，香港真係塊褔地嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}